doc.parameter:
the server type of the server to be used, one 
                            of &apos;sandbox&apos; or &apos;production&apos;.
                            defaults to &apos;sandbox&apos;

the currency of the items to be added to the cart
                         , as of now values can be &apos;USD&apos; or &apos;GBP&apos;.
                         defaults to &apos;USD&apos;

the size of the button, one of &apos;large&apos;, &apos;medium&apos; or
                     &apos;small&apos;.
                     defaults to &apos;large&apos;

the size of the button, one of &apos;large&apos;, &apos;medium&apos; or
                     &apos;small&apos;.
                     defaults to &apos;large&apos;

the size of the button, one of &apos;large&apos;, &apos;medium&apos; or
                     &apos;small&apos;.
                     defaults to &apos;large&apos;

a string with the data that will go in the 
                    merchant-private-data tag or an array that will
                    be mapped to xml, formatted like (e.g.):
                    array(&apos;my-order-id&apos; =&gt; 34234,
                          &apos;stuff&apos; =&gt; array(&apos;registered&apos; =&gt; &apos;yes&apos;,
                                           &apos;category&apos; =&gt; &apos;hip stuff&apos;))
                    this will map to:
                    &lt;my-order-id&gt;
                      &lt;stuff&gt;
                        &lt;registered&gt;yes&lt;/registered&gt;
                        &lt;category&gt;hip stuff&lt;/category&gt;
                      &lt;/stuff&gt;
                    &lt;/my-order-id&gt;

a string with the data that will go in the 
                    merchant-private-item-data tag or an array that will
                    be mapped to xml, formatted like:
                    array(&apos;my-item-id&apos; =&gt; 34234,
                          &apos;stuff&apos; =&gt; array(&apos;label&apos; =&gt; &apos;cool&apos;,
                                           &apos;category&apos; =&gt; &apos;hip stuff&apos;))
                    this will map to:
                    &lt;my-item-id&gt;
                      &lt;stuff&gt;
                        &lt;label&gt;cool&lt;/label&gt;
                        &lt;category&gt;hip stuff&lt;/category&gt;
                      &lt;/stuff&gt;
                    &lt;/my-item-id&gt;
